   <taskbody>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">
               <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Replacing the top part of the mixing arm and/or the outer scraper arm:</b>
            </cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <ul class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Unscrew the adjustment screws (6 &amp; 11) far enough for the spring (8) and
                     plug bolt (4) to be pulled out.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Remove the insertable sheet (10).</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Remove the feather key (7) by moving the adjusting rings (5 &amp; 9) to the
                     side.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Pull the top part of the mixing arm (14) out of the rotor case (12).</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">To reassemble, complete the steps in reverse order.</li>
               </ul>
